----------------------------------------------------------------------

How to build:

./configure [--prefix=/usr]           # default: /usr/local
make


Documentation:

	Can be found in the doc-subdirectory. It's in HTML-format (as this
is highly portabel and a browser shouldn't be to much for a programmer).


Structure:

   - Common:    Contains common classes of general interest.
   - Windows:   Classes and other stuff related to windoze.
   - X-Windows: Classes and other stuff related to X-windows.
   - doc      : Documentation
